# Dragonhold
The Dragonhold is located on top of the surface of the [[Star Sapphire|Star Sapphire]], otherwise known as the cap of the [[Tronjheim|Tronjheim]]. It was large enough to house the [[Dragon|dragons]] and their [[Dragon Rider|Riders]] when visiting.
